                "description": {
                    "value": "<p>A severely damaged flesh golem has a chance of going berserk. If it has 20 or fewer HP at the start of its turn, the golem must succeed at a <span data-pf2-check=\"flat\" data-pf2-dc=\"5\" data-pf2-label=\"Berserk DC\" data-pf2-show-dc=\"gm\">flat check</span> or go berserk. A berserk golem wildly attacks the nearest living creature, or the nearest object if no creatures are nearby.</p>"
